name: Moysenland
description:
Via a portal You arrive in Moysenland! Your goal is to find another portal that will take you back home. Explore the six areas in Moysenland and search for signs and objects that You will need to get there. Activate elevators and moving platforms, open doors and navigate through tunnels.

main Functions:

Control Your Player With Keyboard and Mouse.

Get Game Menu With Esc Key.

Audio settings, Quit and save, How to play, Exit game.

Windowed Mode Is A Choice.
